{"tid":2029425,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美眾議員提法案　授權特朗普承認香港屬獨立國家","createTime":"2020-05-22T08:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T08:50:26.000Z","uid":201464,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a83935bf0b444b72b9c9a7bab5e096dbf6f97057","tid":2029425,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:26:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%AC%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259C%25BE%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%258E%2588%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSklZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=b9ba689c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%259C%25BE%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%258E%2588%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&h=a529cf8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BE%8E%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E6%8E%88%E6%AC%8A%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%AC%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/</a><br />\n<br />\n人大即將審議香港國家安全法草案，將由人大常委會制訂國安法，直接納入基本法附件三，由特區政府宣布實施，不需要經過立法會；美國共和黨眾議員 Scott Perry 在當地時間星期三提出法案，授權總統特朗普承認香港屬獨立國家。<br />\n<br />\n法案在當地時間 5 月 19 日提出，交由眾議院外交事務委員會處理。據眾議院網頁，法案名稱為「授權總統承認中華人民共和國香港特別行政區為一個單獨的獨立國家及其他（To authorize the President to recognize the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region of the People's Republic of China as a separate, independent country, and for other purposes.）」，網頁暫時未有其他法案內容及推行時間表。<br />\n<br />\n提出法案的共和黨 Scott Perry，自 2013 年起出任賓夕法尼亞州眾議員。在反修例運動期間，他曾在社交網頁轉發示威片段，並發文表示支持香港（stand with Hong Kong），批評逃犯條例違反一國兩制，呼籲中國結束專制政府，延續香港的自治（an end to authoritarian government, and the continued autonomy of Hong Kong）。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大會議宣布審議「港版國安法」，美國總統特朗普昨回應稱，中國若在香港香港實行「港版國安法」，將作出強烈回應。美國國務院發言人則警告，違反港人意願在港推行國家安全法，必然會受到美國及國際社會的強烈譴責。"},{"pid":"4dab2871747d686a849ff264ffb75a58eb065476","tid":2029425,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"fa48ea06dbcbe0aa3f578791a343661b27758447","tid":2029425,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"撐呀！！"},{"pid":"0a521f3095b0b304a9a6b5bd36c4fd455dcc6975","tid":2029425,"uid":215740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:43:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9b00c8bcfef4363f9ebc6531b8ce15b2368d2a6","tid":2029425,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"香港民族自決獨立！"}]}